      15.100000381469727
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      67.85,
      206.84,
      540.23,
      247.33
    ],
    "text": "bear in mind the nature and significance of the contradictions, viewed in the light of the whole of the evidence given by the witness. It was further",
