    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      68.25,
      249.31,
      540.5,
      331.81
    ],
    "text": "held that, too great a significance cannot be attached to minor discrepancies or contradictions as by and large a witness cannot be expected to possess a photographic memory and to recall the exact details of an incident.",
    "fonts": [
      "Helvetica"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      13.281599044799805,
      13.882370948791504,
      13.938019752502441,
      14.089996337890625,
      14.100000381469727,
      14.239212989807129,
      14.257817268371582,
      14.446785926818848,
      14.560287475585938,
      14.57993221282959
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.33,
      341.95,
      309.44,
      361.33
    ],
    "text": "It was further held in that case that:-",
    "fonts": [
      "Helvetica"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      13.915239334106445,
      14.05101490020752,
      14.100000381469727,
      14.221823692321777,
      14.2811861038208
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.61,
      371.23,
      539.77,
      390.61
    ],
