    "bbox": [
      68.39,
      392.84,
      540.28,
      454.22
    ],
    "text": "which do not go to the root of the matter and shake the credibility and coherence of the testimonial as a whole. The mere presence of such contradictions therefore, does not have the effect of militating against",
    "fonts": [
      "Helvetica"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      13.408650398254395,
      14.057987213134766,
      14.100000381469727,
