    "bbox": [
      68.25,
      184.52,
      539.33,
      203.9
    ],
    "text": "evidence given by the accused-appellant as true. The learned trial Judge",
    "fonts": [
      "Helvetica"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      13.281599044799805,
      14.100000381469727
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      67.86,
      205.87,
      538.5,
      288.37
    ],
    "text": "in this case had considered the totality of the evidence before he reached the conclusion to reject the evidence given by the accused-appellant is insufficient to create a reasonable doubt in the prosecution case. The prosecution in this case had led clear evidence to prove that the accused-",
    "fonts": [
      "Helvetica"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      13.140289306640625,
      13.854055404663086,
      13.915239334106445,
      13.92354679107666,
      14.00583553314209,
